    public class SimpleHostRoutingFilter
extends com.netflix.zuul.ZuulFilter
    Route ZuulFilter that sends requests to predetermined URLs via apache HttpClient. URLs are found in RequestContext.getRouteHost().
    Author:
    Spencer Gibb, Dave Syer, Bilal Alp, Gang Li
